{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/selecting-from-many-options-with-switch-statements","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Izbor Izmedju Vise Opcija Pomocu switch Iskaza","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ako treba da uporedite jednu vrednost sa vise opcija, mozete koristiti <dfn>switch</dfn> iskaz. <code>switch</code> iskaz poredi vrednost sa <dfn>case</dfn> granama koje predstavljaju moguce vrednosti. Bilo koji validan JavaScript kod moze se izvrsiti unutar <dfn>case</dfn> grane i izvrsavanje traje od prve poklopljene <code>case</code> vrednosti do <code>break</code> naredbe.</p>\n<p>Evo primera <code>switch</code> iskaza:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">switch (fruit) {\n  case \"apple\":\n    console.log(\"The fruit is an apple\");\n    break;\n  case \"orange\":\n    console.log(\"The fruit is an orange\");\n    break;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>case</code> vrednosti se proveravaju strogom jednakošcu (<code>===</code>). <code>break</code> govori JavaScript-u da prekine izvrsavanje. Ako <code>break</code> nedostaje, sledeca naredba ce se izvrsiti.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244dd","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napisi <code>switch</code> iskaz koji testira <code>val</code> i postavlja <code>answer</code> prema sledecim uslovima:\n<code>1</code> - <code>alpha</code>\n<code>2</code> - <code>beta</code>\n<code>3</code> - <code>gamma</code>\n<code>4</code> - <code>delta</code></p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18277,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/selecting-from-many-options-with-switch-statements"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function caseInSwitch(val) {\n  let answer = \"\";\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n\n\n  // Only change code above this line\n  return answer;\n}\n\ncaseInSwitch(1);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>caseInSwitch(1)</code> treba da vrati string <code>alpha</code></p>","testString":"assert(caseInSwitch(1) === 'alpha');"},{"text":"<p><code>caseInSwitch(2)</code> treba da vrati string <code>beta</code></p>","testString":"assert(caseInSwitch(2) === 'beta');"},{"text":"<p><code>caseInSwitch(3)</code> treba da vrati string <code>gamma</code></p>","testString":"assert(caseInSwitch(3) === 'gamma');"},{"text":"<p><code>caseInSwitch(4)</code> treba da vrati string <code>delta</code></p>","testString":"assert(caseInSwitch(4) === 'delta');"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da koristite <code>if</code> ili <code>else</code> iskaze</p>","testString":"assert(!/else/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)) || !/if/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p>Treba da imate najmanje 3 <code>break</code> naredbe</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/break/g).length > 2);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"selecting-from-many-options-with-switch-statements","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/adding-a-default-option-in-switch-statements","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/golf-code","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244dd","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/selecting-from-many-options-with-switch-statements"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}